d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83ee512673aa91492c242eaf02922235d374625","tid":584983,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"中國人一人一篤口水都浸死你！"},{"pid":"c5d3c7a379500ada6ad6a3cbd05031d2200ebde7","tid":584983,"uid":54337,"like":157,"dislike":1,"score":156,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:48:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;成語動畫廊：<br />\n印度版愚公移山&gt;</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n印度佬愚公向鐵橋吐口水，誓要拆左條橋。<br />\n<br />\n印度佬智叟見到，笑鳩愚公：你咪戇鳩啦，你點吐口水都好，條橋都唔會冧。<br />\n<br />\n印度佬愚公輕笑說：我吐口水，條橋唔冧，個任務我交比個仔。個仔吐口水，條橋唔冧，個任務就交比個孫 .... 父傳子，子傳孫，子子孫孫日日吐口水，精誠所致，金石為開，條橋一定冧。<br />\n<br />\n印度佬智叟聞言，啞然無聲。"},{"pid":"1859ef2bb0405aa056d98e726a667279aa53b240","tid":584983,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"47c76f4c70675277576e2cc62f896e23fef6832e","tid":584983,"uid":118623,"like":51,"dislike":7,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:20:49.000Z","msg":"好想奶吓條鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:52:25.000Z","msg":"奶完應該直接入殮房"},{"pid":"59101a9287ef922c81a89c49db687c3b585173b3","tid":584983,"uid":66610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:53:31.000Z","msg":"圍膠板得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7561d046e2117fd30cff234237d7fc32b644fe4","tid":584983,"uid":34623,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"47c76f4c70675277576e2cc62f896e23fef6832e","tid":584983,"uid":118623,"like":51,"dislike":7,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:20:49.000Z","msg":"好想奶吓條鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/200033_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2